          div(class="title") ОБРАТНЫЙ ЗВОНОК
          .popup__inner_callback-form__subtitle Как с вами связаться?
          +call-popup-tabs
          div(class="js-formList")
            div(class="js-feedbackSuccess")
            div(class="form-group field-feedback-user_email required")
              input(type="text" id="feedback-user_email" class="js-spam-email" name="Feedback[user_email]" placeholder="E-mail")
            .popup__inner_callback-form__inputbox
              input(type="tel" id="w23" class="form-control" name="Feedback[telephone]" maxlength="18" placeholder="Телефон" data-plugin-inputmask="inputmask_a55dd1dc")
              .popup__inner_callback-form__country-code +7
              +call-popup-dropdown
            div(class="form-group field-feedback-agree required")
              input(type="hidden" name="Feedback[agree]" value="0")
              input(type="checkbox" id="feedback-agree" name="Feedback[agree]" value="1")
              label(class="control-label" for="feedback-agree") Я согласен <a href="/article/politika-konfidentcialnosti/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:underline">с политикой конфиденциальности</a>  и <a href="/upload/LP_terms.pdf" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:underline">пользовательским соглашением</a>
              div(class="help-block")
            div(class="form-group field-feedback-phone required")
             input(type="text" id="feedback-phone" class="js-spam-phone" name="Feedback[phone]" placeholder="Телефон")
            div(class="form-group field-feedback-feedback_type")
             label(class="control-label" for="feedback-feedback_type")
             input(type="hidden" id="feedback-feedback_type" class="form-control" name="Feedback[feedback_type]" value="1" maxlength="1")
             div(class="help-block")
            button(type="button" class="js-clear-online-spam-form-btn js-send-feedback-form-btn btn btn--outline popup__btn" onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'button', 'click', 'callbackclick '); yaCounter32655285.reachGoal('CALLBACKCLICK'); return true;") Отправить

